metadata.title: Alaska Current Meter and Tide Gauge Data

creators.name: University of Alaska Fairbanks (UAF), School of Fisheries
Ocean Sciences (SFOS), Institute of Marine Science (IMS)

metadata.description: Contains current profiles of Alaskan waters including Gulf of Alaska, Bering Sea, Chukchi Sea, Prince William Sound, Boca de Quadra.  Profiles may contain temperature, pressure, salinity, conductivity, speed, direction of water (current), or air (met) station.
metadata.notes:
